title: Georgia Registered Voters by Race/ethnicity by county, Georgia,
name: Georgia Registered Voters by Race/ethnicity by county, Georgia,
description: Georgia is one of the Super Tsunami Tuesday states that holds primary on 5th February, 2008 along with two dozen other states/territories. Georgia has open primary, i.e., cross-party voting is allowed in Democratic and Republican primaries.The map is based data published on 7th Jan, 2008 by Georgia Secretary of State's office Election division. It shows the number of registered voters by race/ethnicity. Percentage of registered voters of race/ethnic groups has been computed and provided as additional fields for mapping.  Look on GC for other data/maps related to Georgia registered voters. Georgia primary results data/maps will be available after the 5th February, 2008 primary.
